{"tid":1803789,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"新年新口號：「消費就係投票，排隊就係示威」","createTime":"2019-12-30T12:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T13:01:30.000Z","uid":280192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90cbad4ac3ddcb269478bce50dfcb69b0aa9376e","tid":1803789,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:59:41.000Z","msg":"運動進入新階段，亦需要一d新口號：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">消費就係投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n排隊就係示威</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS.1呢個階段嘅成敗，不在於再谷百萬人遊行。而在於百萬人持續不斷將抗爭融入生活之中，考嘅係耐力。生活中自然做左，就係耐力嘅極致。食飯等於抗爭，抗爭等於食飯。孫悟空決戰斯路前，就係將超級撒亞人嘅金色熊熊殺氣火焰，轉化成生活自然狀態，實力先可以進一步增強。<br />\n<br />\nPS2 政府想醜化黃圈，但黃圈其實理念非常崇高，係等於甘地帶印度人去海邊煮鹽。背後嘅理念就係：「我地全部人寧願麻煩少少，都唔L比錢班仆街官商賺，然後榨壓返我地。」<br />\n<br />\nPS3 黃圈其實已經贏緊，但可能我地太少贏，贏左都唔識收割戰果。簡單來講，就係要比對方跪，遠交近攻，門檻先低後高就得。就算店主只係貼連儂牆，都已經好難返轉頭。因為貼左，有咩活動就可以問店主：捐錢參唔參加、義賣日參唔參、大罷工參唔參？多數都會越踩越深。"},{"pid":"55ea7b34bd22b8e65c84910e4f40006fa1f12cc5","tid":1803789,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkWDcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=89a697c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"fon